    parentName: "blockquote"
  }, mdx("em", {
    parentName: "p"
  }, "NOTE:  This was originally written before the release of ChatGPT, so the context of writing it, is different to the context for many who've used chat.openai.com as is now the case.  nonetheless, these public services, are indeed operating publically.  The Webizen systems aim to provide similar functionality, but in a way that's able to support confidential computing"), "."), mdx("p", {
    parentName: "blockquote"
